detected%20a%20suspected%20case%20of%20large-scale%20gold%20smuggling%20involving%20air%20freight%2C%20and%20seized%20about%20146%20kilograms%20of%20suspected%20gold%20with%20an%20estimated%20market%20value%20of%20about%20%2484%20million%2C%20at%20Hong%20Kong%20International%20Airport.%20Photo%20shows%20the%20suspected%20smuggled%20gold%20which%20was%20moulded%20and%20camouflaged%20as%20air%20compressor%20parts.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6615001d16bde8d4ead6cada%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20suspected%20smuggled%20gold%20was%20molded%20and%20camouflaged%20as%20air%20compressor%20parts.%3Cp%3ECustoms%20and%20Excise%20Department%20Hong%20Kong%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHong%20Kong%20customs%20officials%20discovered%20146%20kilograms%20of%20suspected%20gold%20on%20board%20a%20freight%20plane%20headed%20for%20Japan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20say%20it%20is%20the%20largest%20gold-smuggling%20case%20on%20record%20in%20terms%20of%20value.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%2031-year-old%20man%20was%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHong%20Kong%20customs%20officials%20have%20seized%20146%20kilograms%20of%20suspected%20gold%2C%20worth%20more%20than%20%2410%20million%2C%20on%20board%20a%20freight%20plane%20headed%20for%20Japan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20discovery%20is%20the%20largest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-putin-wagner-group-gold-smuggling-sanctions-ukraine-moscow-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egold-smuggling%3C%2Fa%3E%20case%20on%20record%20in%20Hong%20Kong%20in%20terms%20of%20seizure%20value%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Customs%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20precious%20metal%20was%20discovered%20on%2027%20March%20while%20officials%20at%20Hong%20Kong%20International%20Airport%20examined%20two%20air%20compressors%20scheduled%20to%20be%20shipped%20b