f%20the%20People%20Act%2C%201951%20-%20could%20face%20a%20six-month%20prison%20sentence%20and%2For%20get%20a%20fine%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EControversy%20over%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar's%20poll%20affidavit%20broke%20after%20it%20showed%20his%20income%20for%20FY%202021%2F22%20was%20just%20Rs%20680.%20For%20FY20%20and%20FY23%2C%20however%2C%20he%20declared%20incomes%20of%20Rs%2017.5%20lakh%20and%20Rs%205.50%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandrasekhar%20also%20declared%20total%20assets%20worth%20Rs%2028%20crore%3B%20these%20included%20cash%2C%20bank%20deposits%2C%20holdings%20in%20non-banking%20financial%20companies%20and%20cooperative%20societies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20investments%20bonds%2C%20debentures%2C%20shares%2C%20units%20in%20companies%2Fmutual%20funds%2C%20and%20other%20financial%20instruments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20movable%20assets%20included%20a%20vintage%20motorcycle%20-%20a%201942%20Red%20Indian%20Scout%20-%20and%20other%20items%20valued%20at%20an%20estimated%20Rs%203.25%20crore.%20His%20sole%20declared%20immovable%20asset%20was%20a%20plot%20of%20non-agricultural%20land%20in%20Bengaluru%20in%20Karnataka%20worth%20an%20estimated%20Rs%2014.4%20crore.%20The%20opposition%20had%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20Union%20Minister%20did%20not%20disclose%20other%20owned%20real%20estate%2C%20including%20property%20in%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20ruling%20LDF%20has%20also%20claimed%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20neglected%20to%20disclose%20his%20connection%20to%20a%20holding%20company%20called%20Jupiter%20Capital%2C%20despite%20its%20website%20listing%20him%20as%20its%20'founder'.%20It%20has%20alleged%20this%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bhide%20the%20complex%20web%20of%20companies%20used%20to%20hide%20his%20true%20assets%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EALSO%20READ%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Falternative-to-mr-modi-is-shashi-tharoors-reply-to-key-question-5364204%5C%22%20tar