ing%20could%20read%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-duet-ai-attend-meetings-workplace-productivity-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI-produced%20summary%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20event.%20In%20theory%2C%20this%20would%20get%20them%20up%20to%20speed%20without%20requiring%20them%20to%20watch%20or%20listen%20to%20an%20entire%20meeting%20replay%20%E2%80%94%20or%20chase%20down%20colleagues%20to%20catch%20them%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESaving%20time%20on%20meetings%20was%20among%20the%20reasons%20the%20average%20Copilot%20user%20saved%2014%20minutes%20a%20day%2C%20equivalent%20to%20five%20hours%20a%20month%20or%20one-in-a-half%20workweeks%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTell%20your%20people%20not%20to%20worry%20about%20taking%20notes%20or%20listening%20to%20the%20recording%2C%20and%20instead%20ask%20AI%20to%20recap%20the%20key%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20Microsoft%20wrote%20in%20its%20blog%20post.%20%26quot%3BExecutives%20can%20use%20it%20to%20summarize%20long%20documents%20or%20drawn-out%20email%20chains.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20Americans%20think%20meetings%20can%20take%20a%20toll%20on%20their%20productivity.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.atlassian.com%2Fblog%2Fworkplace-woes-meetings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%201%2C000%20US%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-radically-reshape-job-market-global-economy-employee-labor-innovation-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknowledge%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20conducted%20in%20December%202023%20and%20January%20by%20the%20software%20company%20Atlassian%2C%20in%20partnership%20with%20Wakefield%20Research%2C%2073%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20their%20meeting%20slate%20makes%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20their%20work%20done.%20%3Cstrong%3ET%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehe%20survey%20results%20of%20US%20respondents%20were%20provided%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeventy-nine%20percent%20of%20respondents%20said%20they'd%20be%20more%20productive%20at%20their%20jobs%20if%20they%20could%20spend%20less%20time%20in%20meetings.%20What's%20more%2C%2050%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20have%20to%20work%20overtime%20at%20least%20a%20few%20days%20a%20week%20due%20to%20meeting%20overload.%20Most%20respondents%20said%20their%20meetings%20took%20twice%20as%20long%20as%20they%20needed%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20AI%20is%20already%20saving%20some%20workers%20time%2C%20many%20businesses%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeople-are-bored-with-chatgpt-generative-ai-bosses-are-not-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estill%20figuring%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20exactly%20how%20these%20technologies%20can%20add%20value.%20Microsoft's%20research%20suggests%20that%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20meeting%20time%20could%20be%20the%20low-hanging%20fruit%20for%20some%20new%20adopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EAI%20productivity%20boosts%20can%20save%20companies%20money%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20benefits%20could%20take%20time%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpending%20too%20much%20time%20in%20meetings%20isn't%20just%20frustrating%20for%20many%20employees%2C%20the%20impact%20on%20productivity%20can%20have%20a%20significant%20effect%20on%20a%20company's%20bottom%20line.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeetings-remote-work-great-resignation-four-day-week-quiet-quitting-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2022%20study%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20software%20firm%20Otter.ai%20and%20Steven%20Rogelberg%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20organizational%20science%20at%20the%20University%20of%20North%20Carolina%20in%20Charlotte%2C%20found%20that%20the%20average%20company%20%26quot%3Bwasted%26quot%3B%20about%20%2425%2C000%20per%20employee%20by%20scheduling%20them%20for%20unnecessary%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOrganizations%20invest%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20money%20in%20their%20employees%2C%20and%20thus%2C%20in%20the%20meetings%20they%20attend%2C%26quot%3B%20Rogelberg%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20potential%20for%20massive%20cost-savings%E2%80%A6by%20reducing%20unnecessary%20meeting%20attendance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeetings%20summaries%20aren't%20the%20only%20way%20AI%20tools%20are%20helping%20workers%20save%20time.%20A%20survey%20conducted%20by%20HubSpot%20in%202023%20of%20648%20sales%20professionals%20found%20that%20some%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-saving-sales-teams-hours-work-daily-survey-says-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaving%20over%20two%20hours%20a%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20using%20AI%20for%20scheduling%20meetings%2C%20note-taking%2C%20and%20data%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Slack%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fslack.com%2Fblog%2Fnews%2Fnew-slack-research-shows-accelerating-ai-use-at-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%2010%2C000%20global%20desk%20workers%20conducted%20in%20January%20found%20that%2024%25%20had%20tried%20using%20AI%20tools%20on%20the%20job.%20Around%2080%25%20of%20these%20users%20said%20these%20tools%20had%20boosted%20their%20productivity%3A%20Writing%20assistance%2C%20automating%20workflows%2C%20and%20summarizing%20content%20were%20among%20the%20top%20ways%20the%20respondents%20said%20AI%20tools%20added%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20AI's%20potential%20to%20boost%20productivity%2C%20seeing%20the%20benefits%20can%20take%20time.%20Microsoft's%20research%20found%20that%20using%20its%20Copilot%20tool%20for%2011%20weeks%20was%20the%20%26quot%3Bbreakthrough%20moment%26quot%3B%20at%20which%20a%20majority%20of%20users%20reported%20improvement%20across%20four%20areas%3A%20productivity%2C%20work%20enjoyment%2C%20work-life%20balance%2C%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20attend%20fewer%20meetings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20learning%20curve%20that%20can%20come%20with%20AI%20tools%20is%20why%20some%20companies%20are%20providing%20employees%2