0student%20debt%20would%20qualify%20if%20they%20entered%20repayment%20on%20or%20before%20July%201%2C%202005%2C%20and%20borrowers%20with%20graduate%20debt%20would%20qualify%20if%20they%20first%20entered%20repayment%20on%20or%20before%20July%201%2C%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ERelief%20for%20borrowers%20with%20who%20took%20on%20debt%20for%20%26quot%3Blow-financial-value%20programs%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20schools%20that%20lost%20financial%20aid%20eligibility%20or%20were%20found%20to%20have%20defrauded%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3ERelief%20for%20borrowers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-qualifies-student-loan-forgiveness-borrowers-with-hardship-advocacy-groups-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperiencing%20financial%20hardship%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20senior%20administration%20official%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20more%20details%20on%20hardship%20requirements%20will%20be%20released%20in%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20but%20it's%20likely%20to%20address%20those%20who%20are%20at%20high%20risk%20of%20defaulting%2C%20along%20with%20borrowers%20who%20have%20other%20financial%20burdens%20on%20top%20of%20their%20student%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20is%20the%20timeline%20for%20this%20relief%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20said%20it%20expects%20to%20begin%20implementing%20this%20relief%20in%20the%20fall.%20In%20the%20coming%20months%2C%20it%20will%20publish%20the%20proposed%20text%20for%20the%20new%20rules%20to%20the%20Federal%20Register%2C%20after%20with%20the%20public%20will%20have%20an%20opportunity%20to%20submit%20comments%20on%20the%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIs%20this%20relief%20legal%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20plan%20results%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20striking%20down%20Biden's%20first%20attempt%20at%20broad%20debt%20cancellation%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June.%20While%20the%20first%20plan%20used%20the%20HEROES%20Act%20of%202003%2C%20which%20allow