ly%20closing%20on%20Mondays%20and%20Tuesdays%20to%20cut%20operating%20costs%2C%20Vitalie%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitalie%20has%20also%20cut%20portion%20sizes%20to%20save%20money%2C%20including%20stopping%20serving%20unlimited%20soup%20and%20salad.%20He%20said%20the%20previous%20owners%20had%20been%20serving%2016-%20and%2020-ounce%20steaks%2C%20which%20he%20cut%20to%2010%20and%2012-ounce%20portions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20that's%20the%20way%20the%20restaurant%20was%20for%20many%2C%20many%20decades%2C%20so%20I've%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20pushback%20and%20complaints%20about%20cutting%20portion%20sizes%20and%20raising%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20can%20cut%20back%20portion%20sizes%20anymore.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20fast-food%20worker%20excited%20about%20the%20new%20minimum%20wage%3F%20Or%20a%20franchisee%20or%20restaurant%20manager%20worried%20about%20how%20it%20will%20affect%20your%20business%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agdean%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egdean%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fast-food-20-minimum-wage-restaurant-raise-pay-compete-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712655813000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6615076216bde8d4ead6cb92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-fast-food-20-minimum-wage-restaurant-raise-pay-compete-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWhy%20wash%20dishes%20for%20%2415%20or%20%2417%20if%20I%20can%20go%20get%20%2420%20flipping%20burgers%20at%20McDonald's%2C%26quot%3B%20California%20restaurant%20owner%20Sal%20Vitale%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22gdean%40businessinsider.com%20(Grace%20Dean)%2