2C%20the%20company's%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%2C%20has%20been%20busy%20selecting%20content%20creators%20who%20can%20shape%20the%20behaviors%20of%20these%20entities%20via%20prompts.%20Once%20paired%20with%20a%20person%20to%20run%20things%2C%20each%20AI%20influencer%20will%20create%20posts%20and%20videos%20and%20start%20interacting%20with%20its%20audience.%20The%20AI%20learns%20from%20each%20interaction%20and%20uses%20the%20data%20that's%20gathered%20to%20become%20more%20engaging.%20It's%20no%20problem%20for%20an%20AI%20persona%20to%20respond%20to%20every%20comment%20or%20question%20it%20receives%2C%20and%20turn%20that%20into%20instant%20feedback%20for%20whoever%20is%20running%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20model%20of%20influencing%20requires%20far%20less%20time%20from%20real%20people%2C%20and%20it's%20particularly%20suited%20to%20those%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20influencing%20but%20don't%20want%20to%20put%20their%20own%20lives%20up%20for%20consumption.%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20the%20long%20game%20is%20enabling%20more%20and%20more%20creators%20and%20brands%20to%20come%20in%2C%20create%20their%20own%20entity%2C%20manage%20that%20entity%2C%20advocate%20for%20that%20entity%2C%20and%20evolve%20and%20grow%20them%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Dearing%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20brands%2C%20being%20able%20to%20manage%20a%20consistent%20and%20engaging%20social-media%20presence%20at%20a%20low%20cost%20is%20an%20attractive%20pitch%20%E2%80%94%20and%20some%20have%20already%20expressed%20interest%2C%20Dearing%20told%20me.%20She%20sees%20AI%20influencers%20being%20used%20to%20provide%20a%20deep%20level%20of%20information%2C%20support%2C%20and%20guidance%20on%20brands%20and%20products.%20%26quot%3BProduct%20placement%20is%20such%20a%20tiny%20potential%20of%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20it's%20really%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20exchange.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20take%20time%20to%20see%20whether%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-influencers-social-media-make-money-get-instagram-followers-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20personas%20catch%20on%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20initial%20shift%20spells%20trouble%20for%20the%20future%20of%20influencing.%20Dearing%20doesn't%20think%20traditional%20influencers%20will%20disappear%2C%20but%20she%20thinks%20a%20shift%20toward%20AI%20ones%20is%20possible.%20%26quot%3BI%20see%20both%20scenarios%20existing%20for%20some%20period%20of%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20that%20balance%20looks%20like%2C%20who%20knows%3F%26quot%3B%20She%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20maybe%20it's%20an%2080-20%20where%20brands%20get%20really%20excited%20about%20having%20that%20control%26quot%3B%20and%20human%20influencers%20make%20up%20a%20smaller%20portion%20of%20the%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDo%20AI%20influencers%20really%20stand%20a%20chance%20at%20building%20trust%20with%20an%20audience%3F%20Most%20marketing%20experts%20say%20that%20what%20audiences%20really%20want%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcan-ai-replace-influencers-jobs-authenticity-marketing-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20media%20is%20authenticity%3C%2Fa%3E.%20How%20you%20define%20that%20is%20up%20for%20debate%2C%20but%20it's%20clear%20that%20an%20AI-generated%20influencer%20is%20going%20to%20raise%20some%20eyebrows.%20After%20all%2C%20if%20a%20computer%20animation%20is%20promoting%20a%20new%20skincare%20product%2C%20you%20probably%20wouldn't%20trust%20it%20as%20much%20as%20you%20would%20a%20human%20influencer%20swearing%20it%20was%20life-changing.%20On%20the%20flip%20side%2C%20though%2C%20anyone%20who%20has%20found%20themself%20apologizing%20to%20ChatGPT%20knows%20exactly%20how%20quickly%20we%20start%20to%20see%20AI%20as%20human.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F344855525_Close_Encounters_of_the_AI_Kind_Use_of_AI_Influencers_As_Brand_Endorsers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20paper%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Advertising%20found%20that%20AI%20influencers%20%26quot%3Bcan%20produce%20positive%20brand%20benefits%20similar%20to%20those%20produced%20by%20human%20celebrity%20endorsers.%26quot%3B%20But%20it%20also%20found%20that%20when%20things%20went%20wrong%20with%20an%20AI%20influencer%2C%20there%20was%20similar%20reputational%20brand%20damage.%20There's%20potential%20for%20financial%20harm%2C%20too%3A%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftravel%2F2024%2F02%2F18%2Fair-canada-airline-chatbot-ruling%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAir%20Canada%20AI%20chatbot%3C%2Fa%3E%20gave%20incorrect%20information%20about%20a%20discount%20to%20a%20customer.%20A%20tribunal%20ruled%20that%20the%20company%20was%20bound%20by%20that%20and%20had%20to%20provide%20a%20refund.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.emerald.com%2Finsight%2Fcontent%2Fdoi%2F10.1108%2FEJM-12-2019-0949%2Ffull%2Fhtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20European%20Journal%20of%20Marketing%20found%20that%20consumers%20were%20just%20as%20likely%20to%20follow%20an%20AI%20influencer%20as%20a%20human%20influencer%20but%20that%20they%20didn't%20trust%20the%20AI%20influencer%20as%20much.%20They%20were%2C%20however%2C%20more%20likely%20to%20talk%20with%20others%20about%20the%20AI%20influencer%2C%20which%20could%20turn%20out%20to%20be%20a%20positive%20for%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trust%20question%20may%20already%20be%20moot%2C%20though.%20As%20AI%20chatbots%20have%20become%20more%20commonplace%2C%20most%20of%20us%20are%20already%20using%20them%20regularly.%20Chatbots%20are%20used%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpostgraduateeducation.hms.harvard.edu%2Ftrends-medicine%2Fhow-artificial-intelligence-disrupting-medicine-what-means-physicians%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20%3C%2Fa%3Esupport%2C%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Ftechnology-67872693%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etherapy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20to%20warn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.laika13.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eteens%20of%20the%20dangers%20of%20too%20much%20social%20media%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20how%20different%20is%20an%20AI%20influencer%2C%20really%3F%20Was%20the%20Air%20Canada%20customer%20wrong%20to%20trust%20the%20AI%20bot's%20information%3F%20Clearly%2C%20the%20court%20didn't%20think%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20could%20even%20argue%20that%20there's%20something%20%3Cem%3Emore%3C%2Fem%3E%20authentic%20about%20a%20brand%20using%20an%20AI%20entity%20to%20market%20itself%20and%20engage%20with%20people%20than%20a%20human%20turning%20themself%20into%20a%20brand%20to%20appeal%20to%20the%20algorithmic%20robots%20of%20a%20social-media%20platform.%20We%20already%20know%20that%20influencers%20carefully%20craft%20their%20presentation%2C%20often%20with%20a%20manager%20or%20coach.%20Does%20it%20matter%20that%20an%20influencer%20is%20a%20human%20using%20AI%20tools%20or%20an%20AI%20character%20guided%20by%20a%20human%3F%20Either%20way%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20sell%20us%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20social-media-management%20platform%20Hootsuite's%202024%20Social%20Media%20Trends%20report%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20most%20successful%20brands%20will%20redefine%20'authenticity.'%26quot%3B%20The%20focus%20won't%20be%20on%20who%20is%20creating%20the%20content%20but%20on%20whether%20the%20content%20is%20compelling.%20As%20Dearing%20sees%20it%2C%20we're%20moving%20toward%20an%20information-driven%20experience.%20%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20these%20influencers%20become%20a%20really%20lovely%20visual%20way%20to%20engage%20on%20social%20platforms%20that%20are%20more%20knowledge-based%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20experts%20have%20a%20significantly%20more%20pessimistic%20take%3A%20Eric%20Schmidt%2C%20a%20former%20Google%20CEO%2C%20and%20Jonathan%20Haidt%2C%20a%20social%20psychologist%20and%20author%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Ftechnology%2Farchive%2F2023%2F05%2Fgenerative-ai-social-media-integration-dangers-disinformation-addiction%2F673940%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20about%20the%20potential%20for%20%26quot%3Bskillful%20manipulation%20of%20people%20by%20AI%20super-influencers.%26quot%3B%20This%20would%20be%20possible%2C%20they%20suggested%2C%20by%20the%20potential%20for%20generative%20AI%20to%20be%20highly%20personalized%20to%20individual%20wants%2C%20needs%2C%20and%20interests.%20AI%20has%20also%20been%20used%20to%20create%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-deepfake%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeepfakes%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20celebrities%20and%20influencers%20that%20can%20damage%20their%20reputations.%20Already%2C%20there's%20plenty%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mckinsey.com%2Findustries%2Ftechnology-media-and-telecommunications%2Four-insights%2Fhow-generative-ai-could-revitalize-profitability-for-telcos%3Fstcr%3DF2F39173DE9F4241A6119A5C4423FA44%26cid%3Dother-eml-alt-mip-mck%26hlkid%3D0874292832944462a3d432c45cc12bc9%26hctky%3D11159401%26hdpid%3D844a4e4f-9020-4c56-a265-87c7da381f02%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterest%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20marketers%20in%20AI's%20ability%20to%20exploit%20consumer%20cognitive%20biases.%20Essentially%20providing%20marketers%20with%20a%20highly%20targeted%2C%20souped-up%20version%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20human%20influencers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20AI%20does%20catch%20on%20in%20the%20influencer%20world%2C%20Gen%20Z%20and%20Gen%20Alpha%20will%20have%20an%20even%20more%20challenging%20time%20striking%20influencer%20gold.%20What%20holds%20value%20online%20is%20already%20starting%20to%20undergo%20a%20fundamental%20shift%2C%20and%20influence%20will%20be%20up%20for%20grabs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C