%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fdeath-in-paradise-australia-spinoff-female-lead-1235964934%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20You%20Consider%20Me%20Outsider...%26quot%3B%3A%20Hema%20Malini%20Counters%20Congress%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHer%2010-year%20record%20as%20Mathura%20MP%20has%20turned%20her%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Bbrijwasi%26quot%3B%2C%20actor-politician%20Hema%20Malini%20told%20NDTV%20today%20in%20a%20rebuttal%20to%20her%20Congress%20rival's%20%26quot%3Boutsider%26quot%3B%20charge%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMukesh%20Dhangar%2C%20the%20Congress's%20candidate%20in%20the%20temple%20town%2C%20has%20said%20this%20election%20is%20a%20contest%20between%20%26quot%3Bbrijwasi%26quot%3B%20--%20used%20to%20refer%20to%20Mathura%20residents%20--%20and%20%26quot%3Bpravasi%26quot%3B%20(outsider).%20Responding%20to%20the%20barb%20during%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Ms%20Malini%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20become%20a%20brijwasi%20in%2010%20years.%20I%20am%20a%20brijwasi%20anyway%20because%20I%20am%20a%20devotee%20of%20Lord%20Krishna.%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20the%20work%20that%20I%20have%20done%20here.%20I%20am%20from%20here.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20you%20consider%20me%20an%20outsider%2C%20then%20I%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20outsiders%20work%20better.%20The%20people%20who%20live%20here%20don't%20always%20know%20what%20is%20good%20or%20bad%2C%20and%20what%20can%20be%20better%2C%20but%20did%20not%20happen.%20Because%20we%20are%20from%20outside%2C%20we%20see%20more%20and%20have%20more%20experience.%20So%20we%20want%20more%20to%20happen%20here.%20As%20an%20MP%2C%20I%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20things%20done%20here%20by%20coordinating%20with%20ministers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she%20could%20not%20have%20done%20so%20much%20if%20she%20was%20just%20a%20celebrity.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20able%20to%20do%20it%20because%20I%20am%20an%20MP.%20No%20one%20should%20waste%20this%20position.%20Every%20city%20can%20become%20much%20better%20if%20MPs%20work%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20challenges%20she%20faces%20due%20to%20regular%20trips%20between%20Mumbai%20and%20Mathura%2C%20Ms%20Malini%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20has%20become%20a%20habit%20now.%20It%20takes%20eight%20hours%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Delhi%20to%20Mathura.%20I%20have%20done%20it%20so%20many%20times.%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20else%20will%20do%20it.%20I%20am%20very%20much%20dedicated%20to%20this%20place%20and%20I%20want%20to%20do%20my%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Malini%20was%20first%20elected%20from%20Mathura%20in%20the%202014%20general%20election%20that%20brought%20the%20BJP%20to%20power.%20That%20year%2C%20she%20had%20pulled%20off%20a%20stunning%20win%20over%20sitting%20MP%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20leader%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%2C%20defeating%20him%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%203%20lakh%20votes.%20This%20time%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20and%20his%20party%20are%20backing%20her%20after%20RLD's%20entry%20into%20NDA.%20Interestingly%2C%20in%202022%2C%20Mr%20Chaudhary%20was%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20a%20row%20when%20he%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20BJP%20and%20said%20he%20doesn't%20%26quot%3Bwant%20to%20be%20Hema%20Malini%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20how%20the%20equations%20have%20changed%2C%20the%2075-year-old%20leader%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20definitely%20a%20positive%20(development).%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20campaigned%20for%20him%20many%20years%20back%20and%20he%20won.%20And%20then%2C%20I%20came%20here%20and%20we%20were%20on%20opposite%20sides.%20Now%20again%20he%20is%20back.%20And%20it's%20great%2C%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh%20is%20considered%20a%20messiah%20for%20farmers%20and%20our%20party%20also%20focuses%20on%20the%20welfare%20of%20farmers%20and%20the%20poor%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20also%20asked%20Ms%20Malini%20about%20the%20controversy%20around%20Congress%20leader%20Randeep%20Singh%20Surjewala's%20remarks%20on%20her.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20distorting%20facts%20and%20said%20he%20respects%20Ms%20Malini.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20bothered.%20I%20have%20been%20working%20for%2010%20years.%20No%20one%20is%20against%20me.%20We%20are%20all%20friends%2C%20we%20meet%20in%20Parliament.%20Outside%2C%20some%20words%20are%20said%20here%20and%20there.%20Yogi%20ji%20has%20replied.%20We%20stick%20to%20our%20party's%20code%20of%20conduct.%20Other%20parties%20should%20do%20that%20too%20so%20that%20their%20leaders%20don't%20talk%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20response%20to%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20Ms%20Malini's%20support%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20has%20said%20freedom%20of%20expression%20should%20not%20be%20misused%20to%20insult%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Malini%20was%20also%20asked%20about%20BJP's%20Mandi%20candidate%20and%20actor%20Kangana%20Ranaut%2C%20Ms%20Ranaut%2C%20too%2C%20faced%20derogatory%20remarks%20from%20the%20social%20media%20handles%20of%20Congress%20spokesperson%20Surpiya%20Shrinate.%20Ms%20Shrinate%20has%20said%20the%20now-deleted%20posts%20were%20made%20without%20her%20knowledge.%20%26quot%3BShe%20(Kangana)%20is%20clever%20enough%20(to%20handle%20that).%20She%20has%20been%20very%20successful%20as%20an%20actress%2C%20she%20will%20be%20very%20successful%20as%20a%20politician%20too.%20I%20am%20sure%20she%20will%20do%20the%20best%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Malini%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712653200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4jsevm8g_hema-malini-ndtv_625x300_09_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhema-malini-mathura-lok-sabha-seat-if-you-consider-me-outsider-hema-malini-counters-congress-attack-5405245%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Her%2010-year%20record%20as%20Mathura%20MP