ches-new-less-intimidating-version-of-word-game-13111313%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fscrabble-launches-new-less-intimidating-version-of-word-game-13111313%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shreyas%20Iyer%20Admits%20His%20Big%20Mistake%20That%20Cost%20KKR%20Match%20Against%20CSK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20skipper%20Shreyas%20Iyer%20deconstructed%20their%20first%20loss%20of%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%202024%20season%20which%20came%20against%20five-time%20champion%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20at%20the%20MA%20Chidambaram%20Stadium.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20spearheaded%20the%20bowling%20attack%20for%20the%20hosts%20which%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20comprehensive%20seven-wicket%20for%20CSK%20on%20a%20Chepauk%20track%20which%20stayed%20to%20its%20true%20nature%20and%20fell%20on%20the%20slower%20side.%20After%20losing%20Philip%20Salt's%20wicket%20on%20the%20very%20first%20ball%20of%20the%20innings%2C%20KKR%20managed%20to%20finish%20the%20powerplay%20with%20a%20score%20of%2056%2F1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%20point%2C%20KKR%20struggled%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20surface%20and%20toiled%20hard%20for%20putting%20up%20runs%20on%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20personally%20feel%20we%20fell%20short%20in%20terms%20of%20assessing%20the%20wicket.%20We%20were%20phenomenal%20in%20the%20powerplay%20but%20after%20that%2C%20we%20couldn't%20capitalise%2C%20we%20lost%20consecutive%20wickets.%20We%20weren't%20able%20to%20assess%20the%20conditions%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%20It%20completely%20changed%20after%20the%20powerplay%20and%20scoring%20runs%20off%20this%20wicket%20wasn't%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Iyer%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20surface%20that%20saw%20Jadeja%20claim%20three%20wickets%20for%20just%2018%20runs%20in%20his%20four-over%20spell%2C%20KKR%20spinners%20struggled%20to%20find%20the%20rhythm%20against%20CSK%20batters%20and%20conceded%2074%20runs%20in%20just%209.4%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20they%20know%20conditions%20pretty%20well%20and%20they%20bowled%20according%20to%20their%20plan.%20It%20was%20a%20bit%20tacky%2C%20especially%20even%20when%20the%20hard-hitters%20came%20in%2C%20it%20wasn't%20easy%20for%20them%20to%20go%20%5Bbig%5D%20right%20from%20the%20first%20ball.%20It%20changed%20tremendously%20after%20the%20powerplay.%20We%20were%20trying%20to%20construct%20our%20innings%2C%20didn't%20go%20to%20plan.%20We%20take%20those%20learnings%20and%20move%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spin%20trio%20of%20Jadeja%2C%20Maheesh%20Theekshana%20and%20Rachin%20Ravindra%20combined%20to%20bowl%20nine%20overs%2C%20conceded%20just%2050%20runs%20and%20claimed%20four%20wickets%20to%20restrict%20KKR%20to%20a%20sub-par%20total%20of%20137%2F9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20in%20a%20comfortable%20place%20at%20the%20beginning%2C%20we%20thought%20160-170%20would%20be%20a%20great%20score%20on%20this%20wicket.%20Even%20when%20they%20played%20against%20RCB%2C%20the%20conditions%20were%20fairly%20similar.%20So%20that%20was%20our%20plan%20but%20when%20you%20lose%20consecutive%20wickets%2C%20it's%20difficult%20to%20carry%20forward%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20Iyer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20glad%20this%20happened%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20tournament.%20When%20we%20go%20back%2C%20we%20know%20our%20home%20conditions%20pretty%20well.%20We%20need%20to%20analyse%20the%20situations%20and%20need%20to%20make%20the%20best%20use%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20concluded%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20chasing%20138%2C%20CSK%20hardly%20broke%20a%20sweat%20as%20they%20sailed%20to%20a%20comprehensive%207-wicket%20win%20with%20skipper%20Ruturaj%20Gaikwad%20(67*)%20producing%20the%20standout%20performance%20from%20the%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712650260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fl4ounj18_shr