tally%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20the%20huge%20numbers%20of%20tourists%2C%20residents%20say.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpopular-british-holiday-destination-collapsing-socially-and-environmentally-13111306%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpopular-british-holiday-destination-collapsing-socially-and-environmentally-13111306%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpopular-british-holiday-destination-collapsing-socially-and-environmentally-13111306%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM's%20Takedown%20Of%20Congress%20Features%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20Statue%20Of%20Unity%2C%201984%20Riots%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBJP%20veteran%20Kalyan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20in%201992%2C%20%26quot%3Bdedicated%20his%20life%20and%20government%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20BJP%20rally%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Pilibhit%20in%20support%20of%20party%20candidate%20Jitin%20Prasada%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOur%20Kalyan%20Singh%20ji%20dedicated%20his%20life%20and%20government%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple.%20Every%20family%20of%20the%20country%20contributed%20(to%20the%20temple).%20But%20those%20in%20the%20INDI%20alliance%20have%20always%20hated%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20Was%20Kalyan%20Singh%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Governor%20of%20Rajasthan%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20before%20his%20death%20in%202021%2C%20was%20Chief%20Minister%20when%20the%2016th%20century%20Babri%20Masjid%20was%20demolished%20by%20Hindu%20activists%20at%20Ayodhya.%20Hours%20after%20the%20demolition%2C%20he%20stepped%20down%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20PV%20Narasimha%20Rao%20government%20dismissed%20the%20state%20government%20on%20the%20same%20day%20and%20imposed%20President's%20Rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20second%20term%20as%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20Mr%20Singh's%20government%20withdrew%20cases%20against%20the%20accused%20in%20the%20Babri%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20left%20the%20BJP%20several%20times%20and%2C%20at%20one%20point%2C%20also%20aligned%20himself%20with%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav-led%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20In%202014%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20the%20BJP%20for%20good%20and%20went%20on%20to%20serve%20as%20Governor%20in%20two%20states.%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20among%20top%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20veteran%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%2C%20who%20were%20acquitted%20by%20a%20CBI%20special%20court%20in%202020%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition%20case.%20The%20court%20then%20said%20the%20demolition%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20pre-planned%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Temple%20Charge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20leaving%20no%20stone%20unturned%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20was%20not%20built%20in%20Ayodha.%20%26quot%3BBut%20when%20people%20donated%20every%20penny%20they%20could%20and%20a%20grand%20temple%20was%20constructed%2C%20the%20temple's%20authorities%20forgave%20you%20(Congress)%20and%20invited%20you%20for%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%20But%20you%20rejected%20the%20invitation%20and%20insulted%20Lord%20Ram.%20The%20leaders%20who%20attended%20the%20ceremony%20were%20expelled%20for%20six%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20banking%20on%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20construction%20to%20reap%20dividends%20in%20these%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20politically-significant%20state%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20This%20time%2C%20the%20party%20has%20dropped%20its%20sitting%20Pilibhit%20MP%20Varun%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20raised%20eyebrows%20for%20his%20remarks%20criticising%20the%20government%2C%20and%20has%20chosen%20Mr%20Prasada%2C%20who%20switched%20from%20the%20Congress%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Statue%20Of%20Unity%20Jab%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETargeting%20the%20Opposition%20from%20the%20Pilibhit%20stage%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20the%20Congress%20and%20other%20INDIA%20bloc%20parties%20%26quot%3Bdo%20not%20hesitate%20to%20insult%20great%20personalities%20of%20the%20country%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BNo%20prominent%20leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20or%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20visited%20the%20Statue%20of%20Unity.%20They%20travel%20abroad%2C%20but%20do%20not%20visit%20the%20statue%20of%20Sardar%20(Vallabhbhai%20Patel)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Statue%20of%20Unity%2C%20a%20182-metre%20statue%20of%20the%20country's%20first%20Home%20Minister%2C%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20in%202018%20near%20Gujarat's%20Kevadia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20for%20joining%20hands%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20also%20brought%20up%20the%201984%20anti-Sikh%20riots%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20assassination%20of%20Indira%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BNo%20one%20can%20forget%20what%20the%20Congress%20did%20to%20our%20Sikh%20brothers%20in%201984.%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20supporting%20that%20Congress%20now.%20The%20BJP%20is%20firmly%20with%20Sikhs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712649960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F45hcpb9o_pm-modi-pilibhit_625x300_09_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-2024-lok-sabha-election-kalyan-singh-dedicated-life-government-to-ram-temple-pms-high-praise-5404784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BJP%20veteran%20late%20Kalyan%20Singh%2C%20who%20was%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Uttar%20