5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESharad%20Pawar%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray's%20Sena%20will%20also%20contest%20four%20of%20Mumbai's%20six%20seats%20-%20North%20West%2C%20South%20Central%2C%20South%2C%20and%20South%20East%20seats.%20The%20Congress%20will%20contest%20the%20other%20two%20-%20North%20and%20North%20Central.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20election%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20the%20(then%20undivided)%20Sena%20won%20three%20each%3B%20the%20two%20were%20allies%20then%20but%20fell%20out%2C%20in%20dramatic%20fashion%20after%20the%20Assembly%20election%20later%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhiwandi%2C%20Sangli%20Row%20Settled%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bhiwandi%20and%20Sangli%20seats%20-%20which%20all%20three%20claimed%2C%20threatening%20to%20derail%20talks%20-%20have%20been%20given%20to%20Mr%20Pawar's%20NCP%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray's%20Sena.%20Congress%20leader%20Nana%20Patole%20called%20the%20issue%20%26quot%3Bresolved%26quot%3B%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20our%20workers%20will%20work%20to%20make%20the%20MVA%20candidates%20victorious%20in%20both%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20we%20saw%20what%20(this)%20dictatorial%20government%20(a%20reference%20to%20the%20BJP)%20has%20been%20doing.%20Our%20workers%20have%20worked%20wholeheartedly%2C%20across%20the%20country%2C%20to%20fight%20against%20these%20dictatorial%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Congress'%20Maharashtra%20unit%20boss%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20aim%20is%20to%20throw%20out%20the%20BJP.%20We%20will%20work%20for%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20comes%20a%20time%20when%20we%20have%20to%20move%20forward...%20we%20have%20reached%20this%20deal%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20winning%20the%20election.%20We%20have%20done%20this...%20now%20the%20people%20will%20decide%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20said%20candidates%20(for%20s