%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi's%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20today%20extended%20the%20judicial%20custody%20of%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha%20-%20arrested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20-%20till%20April%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EK%20Kavitha%20-%20the%20daughter%20of%20former%20Telangana%20Chief%20Minister%20K%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20-%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2015%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20which%20is%20investigating%20the%20money%20laundering%20angle%20in%20the%20alleged%20scam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Ee%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20which%20had%20begun%20the%20initial%20investigation%20into%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20has%20also%20been%20allowed%20her%20to%20question%20in%20the%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Kavitha%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20court%2C%20said%20that%20the%20investigation%20by%20central%20agencies%20-%20which%20she%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bmedia%20trial%26quot%3B%20-%20has%20hit%20her%20reputation%20and%20invaded%20her%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20victim.%20My%20personal%20and%20political%20reputation%20has%20been%20targeted.%20My%20mobile%20phone%20is%20displayed%20on%20all%20television%20channels%2C%20directly%20invading%20my%20privacy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20letter%20which%20was%20read%20out%20in%20the%20court%20by%20her%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20cooperated%20with%20the%20agencies%20and%20given%20all%20the%20bank%20account%20details.%20I%20will%20hand%20over%20all%20the%20mobile%20phones%20which%20the%20ED%20claim%20that%20I%20have%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20earlier%20refused%20to%20permit%20K%20Kavitha%20to%20address%20the%20court%20personally%20and%20said%20that%20she%20could%20give%20her%20requests%20in%20written%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20alleged%20misuse%20of%20the%20central%20agencies%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20Ms%20Kavitha%20in%20the%20letter%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B95%20per%20cent%20cases%20of%20ED%2FCBI%20are%20against%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20and%20when%20the%20accused%20Joins%20BJP%20the%20investigation%20abruptly%20stops.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20leaving%20the%20court%2C%20the%20BRS%20leader%20said%20that%20the%20case%20against%20her%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20case%20completely%20based%20on%20the%20statement.%20It%20is%20a%20political%20case.%20This%20is%20a%20case%20of%20targeting%20the%20opposition%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712649480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fp9qbt85_k-kavitha-rouse-avenue-court_625x300_05_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-kavitha-brs-k-chandrashekar-rao-delhi-liquor-policy-case-reputation-hit-privacy-invaded-k-kavitha-in-letter-to-court-5404664%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Delhi%20court%20today%20extended%20the%20judicial%20custody%20of%20BRS%20leader%20K%20Kavitha's%20till%20April%2023%20in%20judicial%20custody.%20She%20was%20arrested%20on%20March%2015%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-kavitha-brs-k-chandrashekar-rao-delhi-liquor-policy-case-reputation-hit-privacy-invaded-k-kavitha-in-letter-to-court-5404664%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-kavitha-brs-k-chandrashekar-rao-delhi-liquor-policy-case-reputation-hit-privacy-invaded-k-kavitha-in-letter-to-court-5404664%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fk-kavitha-brs-k-chandrashekar-rao-delhi-liquor-policy-case-reputation-hit-privacy-invaded-k-kavitha-in-letter-to-court-5404664%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2