%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-veteran-ak-antony-wishes-his-son-who-joined-bjp-loses-elections-5404619%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-veteran-ak-antony-wishes-his-son-who-joined-bjp-loses-elections-5404619%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20oil%20dominates%20India%E2%80%99s%20oil%20imports%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712649060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109157585%2Cimgsize-187690.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Frussian-oil-dominates-indias-oil-imports-share-of-iraq-saudi-arabia-uae-and-us-falls%2Farticleshow%2F109156464.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Russia's%20crude%20oil%20imports%20to%20India%20surged%20to%2035%25%20in%20FY24%20from%2023%25%20the%20previous%20year%2C%20surpassing%20other%20major%20suppliers%20like%20Iraq%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20UAE%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20Russian%20supply%20rose%20to%201.57%20million%20barrels%20a%20day%2C%20while%20Iraq%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20experienced%20declines.%20Despite%20challenges%2C%20Indian%20refiners%20favor%20Russian%20crude%20for%20discounts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20No%20Pay%2C%20Pak%20Finance%20Minister%20Leaves%20Banker%20Life%20Behind%20To%20Fix%20Economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPakistan's%20new%20finance%20minister%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20fix%20his%20country.%20To%20many%2C%20it's%20an%20unenviable%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuhammad%20Aurangzeb%20took%20up%20the%20post%20last%20month%20at%20a%20time%20when%20Pakistan's%20economy%20is%20enduring%20the%20most%20turbulent%20period%20in%20its%20history.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELurching%20from%20one%20bailout%20program%20to%20the%20next%20with%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%20classifying%20its%20debt%20as%20only%20borderline%20sustainable%2C%20Pakistan%20has%20Asia's%20fastest%20inflation%2C%20anemic%20growth%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20tax-collection%20rates%20in%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20prominent%20banker%20and%20JPMorgan%20Chase%20%26amp%3B%20Co.%20alumnus%2C%20Aurangzeb%20comes%20as%20well%20equipped%20as%20any%20of%20his%20predecessors%20to%20face%20the%20challenge.%20But%20that's%20to%20disregard%20an%20array%20of%20extra%20factors%20affecting%20the%20role%20which%20are%20outside%20his%20control%2C%20including%20volatile%20domestic%20politics%2C%20tensions%20with%20neighbors%20India%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Iran%2C%20and%20a%20catastrophic%20position%20on%20the%20front%20line%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBroadly%2C%20the%20finance%20minister's%20job%20is%20to%20manage%20and%20steer%20the%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mosharraf%20Zaidi%2C%20a%20former%20government%20adviser%20and%20founder%20of%20policy%20think%20tank%20Tabadlab%20based%20in%20Pakistan's%20capital%2C%20Islamabad.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20simple%20when%20framed%20this%20way.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20complex%20jobs%20on%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20most%20immediate%20of%20his%20tasks%20is%20to%20seal%20a%20deal%20by%20June%20with%20the%20IMF%20for%20a%20minimum%20three%20year%20program%20worth%20at%20least%20%246%20billion.%20Key%20objectives%20in%20the%20negotiations%20for%20the%20fund%20will%20include%20broadening%20the%20tax%20base%2C%20improving%20debt%20sustainability%20and%20restoring%20viability%20to%20the%20energy%20sector%20-%20all%20steps%20that%20Pakistan%20has%20avoided%20for%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurangzeb%20cites%20a%20shared%20sense%20of%20urgency%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%2C%20who%20was%20elected%20to%20a%20second%20successive%20term%20in%20March.%20%26quot%3BHe's%20a%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20get%20things%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20Sharif%20in%20an%20interview%20in%20his%20ministry%20in%20Islamabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20time%20to%20actually%20capitalize%20on%20that%20mandate%20and%20ensure%20that%20all%20the%20tough%20decisions%20that%20need%20to%20be%20taken%20are%20taken%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Aurangzeb.%20The%20alternative%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Ba%20huge%20missed%20opportunity%20that%20we%20can%20ill%20afford.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20consult%20with%20everyone%2C%20we%20should%20try%20to%20build%20a%20consensus%2C%20but%20a%20few%20things%20we'll%20just%20have%20to%20bite%20the%20bullet%20and%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20a%20prominent%20family%20in%20Lahore%20-%20his%20father%20was%20Pakistan's%20attorney%20general%20-%20Aurangzeb%2C%2059%2C%20went%20to%20the%20nation's%20elite%20Aitchison%20College%20then%20studied%20at%20Wharton%20on%20a%20scholarship%20before%20working%20at%20Citigroup%20Inc.%20in%20New%20York%20early%20in%20his%20career.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20returned%20to%20Pakistan%20to%20work%20at%20a%20unit%20of%20ABN%20Amro%20Bank%20NV%2C%20later%20shifting%20to%20the%20bank's%20headquarters%20in%20Amsterdam.%20In%202018%2C%20he%20again%20accepted%20a%20move%20back%20to%20his%20home%20country%20when%20he%20left%20JPMorgan%20in%20Singapore%20to%20take%20over%20as%20chief%20executive%20officer%20of%20Pakistan's%20largest%20lender%2C%20Habib%20Bank%20Ltd.%2C%20just%20after%20it%20had%20been%20fined%20%24225%20million%20and%20forced%20to%20end%20its%20US%20operations%20for%20weak%20anti-money-laundering%20controls%20and%20sanctions%20compliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20his%20return%20to%20Pakistan%20surprised%20those%20he%20worked%20with%2C%20since%20he%20was%20seen%20to%20be%20leaving%20the%20comfort%20of%20Singapore%20and%20a%20cushy%20role%20at%20JPMorgan%20for%20a%20post%20that%20few%20considered%20a%20dream%20job%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20colleague.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurangzeb%20would%20often%20speak%20about%20his%20love%20for%20the%20country%20of%20his%20birth%20and%20the%20elevation%20to%20finance%20minister%20is%20seen%20as%20evidence%20of%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20nation%2C%20the%20person%20said%2C%20asking%20not%20to%20be%20named%20discussing%20personal%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarried%20with%20two%20adult%20children%2C%20Aurangzeb%20-%20also%20known%20as%20Auri%20-%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20prime%20minister's%20economic%20advisory%20council%20in%202022%20during%20Sharif's%20previous%20term%2C%20a%20role%20that%20gave%20him%20an%20inside%20view%20of%20the%20premier's%20management%20style.%20He%20was%20tapped%20for%20the%20finance%20post%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20the%20election%2C%20flying%20from%20his%20base%20in%20the%20commercial%20capital%20Karachi%20to%20meet%20with%20Sharif%20multiple%20times%20before%20accepting%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20huge%20privilege%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20set%20of%20expectations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeats%20of%20Power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20ministry%20sits%20close%20to%20the%20Margalla%20hills%20that%20bound%20the%20capital%20to%20the%20north%2C%20a%2020%20minute%20walk%20from%20the%20prime%20minister's%20office%2C%20with%20the%20national%20assembly%20midway%20between%20the%20two%20seats%20of%20government%20power.%20A%20recent%20introduction%20to%20his%20office%20is%20a%20large%20television%20with%20split%20screens%20showing%20stock%20market%20prices%2C%20economic%20indicators%2C%20and%20Bloomberg%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurangzeb%20was%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20paid%20corporate%20leaders%20in%20Pakistan%20before%20joining%20the%20government.%20Now%2C%20in%20line%20with%20other%20cabinet%20members%2C%20he's%20not%20drawing%20a%20salary.%20He%20also%20renounced%20his%20Dutch%20citizenship%20to%20become%20eligible%20for%20the%20post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20he%20describes%20as%20%26quot%3Bnational%20service%26quot%3B%20will%20mean%20reaching%20tough%20decisions%20under%20the%20toughest%20IMF%20program%20in%20years%20if%20he%20and%20Sharif%20are%20to%20bring%20the%20economy%20back%20from%20the%20brink.%20These%20include%20putting%20a%20stop%20to%20accumulating%20more%20state%20losses%20by%20raising%20energy%20prices%20and%20selling%20state-owned%20companies%2C%20unpopular%20choices%20that%20will%20inevitably%20trigger%20pushback%20from%20powerful%20business%20lobbies%20and%20stoke%20public%20anger%20-%20a%20chief%20reason%20they've%20been%20avoided%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurangzeb%20will%20approach%20the%20challenge%20as%20a%20political%20outsider.%20He%20is%20not%20part%20of%20Sharif's%20political%20party%2C%20and%20was%20appointed%20in%20a%20technocratic%20capacity.%20Sharif%20leads%20a%20shaky%20coalition%20whose%20two%20main%20allies%20have%20said%20they%20will%20support%20the%20government%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis%20only.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFresh%20Face%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20already%20been%20attempts%20to%20contain%20Aurangzeb's%20role.%20Sharif%20decided%20to%20chair%20the%20Economic%20Coordination%20Committee%2C%20a%20top%20policy-making%20forum%20that%20is%20usually%20headed%20by%20the%20finance%20minister%2C%20before%20backtracking%20a%20day%20later%20after%20public%20criticism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForeign%20Minister%20Ishaq%20Dar%20-%20a%20veteran%20politician%20who%20served%20four%20separate%20stints%20as%20finance%20minister%20until%20he%20was%20shunted%20sideways%20by%20Sharif%20-%20has%20been%20installed%20as%20head%20of%20a%20privatization%20committee%20that%20would%20normally%20have%20been%20led%20by%20Aurangzeb%20or%20the%20minister%20for%20privatization.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20ministers%20routinely%20swapped%20out%20and%20back%20in%20again%2C%20his%20is%20the%20first%20fresh%20face%20at%20the%20finance%20ministry%20in%20six%20years.%20Finance%20ministers%20are%20regularly%20blamed%20for%20Pakistan's%20economic%20woes%2C%20and%20there%20have%20been%20more%20than%2010%20in%20the%20past%20decade%3B%20Sharif%20had%20two%20in%20his%20previous%2016-month%20tenure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAurangzeb%20is%20clear%20that%20his%20key%20challenge%20is%20the%20economy%20and%20not%20politics.%20For%20all%20his%20corporate%20experience%2C%20he%20says%20he's%20focused%20on%20Pakistan's%20future%20rather%20than%20dwelling%20on%20his%20past%20achievements.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20push%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20get%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712648940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fr2diplr_muhammad-aurangzeb-bloomberg_625x300_09_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwith-no-pay-pakistan-finance-minister-muhammad-aurangzeb-leaves-banker-life-behind-to-fix-economy-5404838%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan's%20new%20finance%20minister%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20fix%20his%20country.%20To%20many%2C%20it's%20an%20unenviable%20task.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwith-no-pay-pakistan-finance-minister-muhammad-aurangzeb-leaves-banker-life-behind-to-fix-economy-5404838%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwith-no-pay-pakistan-finance-minister-muhammad-aurangzeb-leaves-banker-life-behind-to-fix-economy-5404838%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22http