engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fhuman-rights-violated-by-climate-change-inaction-european-court-rules-13111293%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhuman-rights-violated-by-climate-change-inaction-european-court-rules-13111293%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fhuman-rights-violated-by-climate-change-inaction-european-court-rules-13111293%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22New%20Zealand's%20Visa%20Curbs%20Likely%20To%20Hit%20Indian%20Immigrants%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20cue%20from%20Australia%20and%20Canada%2C%20New%20Zealand%20has%20announced%20tighter%20visa%20rules%20to%20check%20the%20number%20of%20immigrants%2C%20increasing%20the%20requirements%20to%20qualify%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20these%20additional%20requirements%20remains%20in%20question%2C%20the%20move%20is%20likely%20to%20impact%20Indians%20seeking%20jobs%20in%20New%20Zealand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20requirements%20include%20English%20proficiency%2C%20work%20experience%20and%20skill%20criteria%2C%20besides%20reducing%20the%20duration%20of%20stay%20with%20a%20work%20permit.%20By%20overhauling%20the%20immigration%20system%2C%20the%20New%20Zealand%20government%20hopes%20to%20control%20the%20%26quot%3Bunsuitable%26quot%3B%20number%20of%20migrants%20entering%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJournalist%20Dita%20De%20Boni%20of%20the%20National%20Business%20Review%20in%20Auckland%20expressed%20concern%20that%20it%20might%20be%20tougher%20for%20Indians%20and%20other%20immigrants%20to%20get%20jobs.%20%26quot%3BThe%20new%20rules%20being%20introduced%20in%20New%20Zealand%20will%20inevitably%20make%20it%20harder%20for%20Indian%20and%20other%20immigrants%20from%20countries%20outside%20the%20Anglosphere%20to%20come%20and%20work%20here.%20Whether%20or%20not%20that%20is%20the%20intention%2C%20however%2C%20is%20hard%20to%20tell%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20comment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20steady%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20Indians%20in%20New%20Zealand.%20As%20per%20the%202018%20New%20Zealand%20census%2C%20Indians%20made%20up%20about%204.7%25%20of%20the%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20in%20October%202023%20said%20New%20Zealand%20has%20approximately%202%2C50%2C000%20persons%20of%20Indian%20origin%20and%20NRIs%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20settled%20there%20permanently.%20Data%20on%20ENZ.org%20(a%20New%20Zealand%20government%20affiliate)%20indicates%20that%20approximately%2018%2C000%20Indians%20have%20migrated%20to%20the%20country%20since%202011.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Zealand's%20Immigration%20minister%20Erica%20Stanford%20announced%20the%20changes%20to%20the%20Accredited%20Employer%20Worker%20Visa%20(AEWV)%2C%20which%20serves%20as%20the%20main%20temporary%20work%20visa.%20It%20was%20introduced%20in%202022%20to%20alleviate%20workforce%20shortages%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%20and%20lockdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20main%20changes%20have%20been%20proposed%20in%20the%20visa%20rules.%20First%2C%20English-language%20requirements%20will%20be%20enforced%20for%20low-skill%20jobs.%20Next%2C%20most%20work%20visas%20will%20require%20a%20minimum%20threshold%20of%20skills%2C%20in%20the%20form%20of%20work%20experience%20or%20suitable%20qualifications.%20Last%2C%20the%20maximum%20continuous%20stay%20allowed%20on%20work%20permits%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20three%20years%20from%20five.%20Employers%20are%20also%20encouraged%20to%20hire%20immigrants%20only%20after%20making%20sure%20that%20there%20are%20no%20%26quot%3Bsuitable%20and%20available%20New%20Zealander%26quot%3B%20candidates%20who%20have%20applied%20for%20the%20job.%20It%20aims%20to%20not%20only%20control%20immigration%2C%20but%20also%20to%20provide%20more%20employment%20to%20locals%20and%20incentivise%20them%20to%20stay%20in%20the%20country.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20country%20recorded%20a%20loss%20of%2047%2C000%20citizens%20who%20moved%20elsewhere%20for%20better%20work%20opportunities.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Immigration%20minister%20claimed%20the%20visa%20restrictions%20would%20be%20beneficial%20for%20migrant%20rights.%20Citing%20previous%20instances%20of%20exploitation%20by%20some%20New%20Zealand%20employers%20who%20were%20misusing%20the%20AEWV%20scheme%20to%20take%20money%20from%20aspiring%20immigrants%2C%20Erica%20Stanford%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BBy%20having%20an%20English-language%20requirement%20migrants%20will%20be%20better%20able%20to%20understand%20their%20rights%20or%20raise%20concerns%20about%20an%20employer%20early.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20these%20changes%2C%20Dita%20De%20Boni%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Minister%20of%20Immigration%20said%20the%20rule%20was%20put%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20migrant%20exploitation%2C%20which%20is%20an%20issue%20New%20Zealand%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20for%20several%20years%2C%20and%20which%20appears%20to%20be%20getting%20worse.%20However%2C%20some%20commentators%20here%20believe%20upping%20the%20English%20language%20requirement%20-%20like%20Australia%20did%20-%20does%20little%20to%20prevent%20exploitation%20happening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20government%2C%20she%20added%2C%20was%20elected%20on%20a%20pro-immigration%20platform%20and%20usually%20had%20the%20support%20of%20the%20business%20sector.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20on%20this%20issue%20it%20might%20be%20different%20-%20%C2%A0Business%20NZ%2C%20which%20represents%20the%20country's%20business%20sector%2C%20is%20wary%20of%20the%20changes%20(not%20just%20the%20enhanced%20English%20language%20but%20other%20changes%20that%20see%20paths%20to%20residency%20in%20certain%20sectors%20such%20as%20construction%20restricted)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712648100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fh1o0ifi4_new-zealand-generic-unsplash_625x300_15_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealands-visa-curbs-likely-to-hit-indian-immigrants-5404773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20a%20cue%20from%20Australia%20and%20Canada%2C%20New%20Zealand%20has%20announced%20tighter%20visa%20rules%20to%20check%20the%20number%20of%20immigrants%2C%20increasing%20the%20requirements%20to%20qualify%20for%20jobs%20in%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealands-visa-curbs-likely-to-hit-indian-immigrants-5404773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealands-visa-curbs-likely-to-hit-indian-immigrants-5404773%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fnew-zealands-visa-curbs-likely-to-hit-indian-immigrants-5404773%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jackie%20Chan%20shares%20health%20update%20after%20concerns%20raised%20over%20his%20appearance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712647920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F04%2F768x432%2Fskynews-jackie-chan-2019_6515463.jpg%3F20240409083936%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjackie-chan-shares-health-update-after-concerns-raised-over-his-appearance-13111286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jackie%20Chan%20has%20reassured%20fans%20after%20concerns%20were%20raised%20about%20his%20appearance%20in%20photographs%20published%20earlier%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fjackie-chan-shares-health-update-after-concerns-raised-over-his-appearance-13111286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2