%20son%2C%20opened%20the%20door.%20The%20second%20she%20opened%20the%20door%2C%20he%20charged%20in%20and%20started%20stabbing%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20Judd%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20sensitive%20nature%20of%20the%20evidence%2C%20authorities%20did%20not%20release%20the%20audio%20recording%20from%20within%20the%20home.%20However%2C%20Sheriff%20Judd%20described%20Elvia%20Espinoza's%20voice%20calling%20out%20%26quot%3BManny%26quot%3B%20repeatedly%20during%20the%20incident%2C%20while%20the%20suspect%20reportedly%20remained%20silent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20made%20the%20statement%20that%20he%20knew%20where%20to%20stab%20her%20for%20maximum%20effect%20because%20of%20his%20biology%20classes%2C%26quot%3B%20Judd%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sheriff%20said%20that%20Manny%20was%20described%20as%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenius%2C%20remarkably%20brilliant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EPolk%20County%20Jail%20mugshot%20for%20Emmanuel%20Espinoza%2C%20DOB%2006%2F12%2F2002%20-%20charged%20with%20First%20Degree%20murder%20in%20the%20stabbing%20death%20of%20his%2046-year-old%20mother%20Elvia%20Espinoza%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtRxxqTGkCZ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FtRxxqTGkCZ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FTs3lsi73dU%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FTs3lsi73dU%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Polk%20County%20Sheriff%20%F0%9F%9A%94%20Grady%20Judd%20(%40PolkCoSheriff)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPolkCoSheriff%2Fstatus%2F1776943299015610569%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%207%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheriff%20Judd%20stated%20that%20the%20investigation%20revealed%20the%20attack%20involved%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20stab%20wounds%20inflicted%20upon%20the%20victim.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20assault%20continued%2