nsume%20millet.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20know%20more%20about%20them%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20an%20aunt%20who%20worked%20in%20the%20food%20science%20department%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20She%20was%20the%20one%20who%20told%20me%20how%20they%20are%20poised%20to%20become%20the%20next%20big%20thing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20with%20his%20gut%20and%20his%20aunt%E2%80%99s%20advice%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338546%2Fmillet-startup-revenue-in-crores-ready-to-eat-food-health-sutra-hyderabad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20started%20Health%20Sutra%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20true%20enough%2C%20even%20the%20Indian%20government%20designated%20it%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9CYear%20of%20Millets%E2%80%9D.%20The%20company%20sells%20cereal%20flakes%20such%20as%20Jowar%20Flakes%2C%20Ragi%20Flakes%2C%20and%20Barley%20Flakes%2C%20as%20well%20as%20seven%20different%20types%20of%20%3Cem%3Erava%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20%3Cem%3Eidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eupma%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20biscuits%20made%20from%20ragi%20and%20jowar.%20The%20brand%20has%20clocked%20an%20impressive%20annual%20revenue%20of%20Rs%202.5%20crores%20since%20its%20inception.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sai%20created%20Health%20Sutra%20to%20bring%20millet%20alternatives%20to%20the%20market.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Health%20Sutra.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fnpi-9-1705584781-500x2