%20few%20days%2C%20she%20saw%20that%20this%20caterpillar%20had%20transformed%20into%20a%20beautiful%20butterfly.%20After%20that%20incident%2C%20she%20became%20so%20fond%20of%20butterflies%20that%20she%20started%20reading%20about%20them.%20This%20newfound%20passion%20led%20her%20to%20create%20a%20small%20ecosystem%20within%20her%20high-rise%20apartment%2C%20where%20she%20rears%20butterflies%20on%20the%2013th%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20Priyanka%20claims%20to%20have%20nurtured%20over%205%2C000%20butterflies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20tailed%20jay%2C%20lime%20swallowtail%2C%20common%20mormon%2C%20red%20pierrot%2C%20blue%20tiger%2C%20salmon%20arab%2C%20and%20lime%20blue.%20She%20adds%20that%20rare%20species%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20apefly%20butterfly%20and%20sunbeam%20butterfly%20%E2%80%94%20visit%20to%20lay%20their%20eggs%2C%20while%20others%20like%20the%20painted%20lady%2C%20common%20grass%20butterfly%2C%20common%20emigrant%2C%20common%20leopard%20butterfly%2C%20palm%20bob%2C%20and%20blank%20swift%20frequent%20the%20space%20for%20nectaring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Butterflies%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fgreen-hope-1712213006-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%2