0and%20Panda%20enthusiastically%20joined%20in.%20It%20sheds%20light%20on%20Mangobindo%E2%80%99s%20generosity%20as%20he%20provided%20food%20to%20hundreds%20of%20those%20who%20were%20starving%20during%20the%20Bengal%20famine%20of%201943.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20these%2C%20Arunangshu%20has%20heard%20many%20stories%20of%20how%20Bose%20loved%20the%20%3Cem%3Epuishaak-er%20chochchori%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Emurighanta%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20Bengali%20fish%20delicacy).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20day%20begins%20in%20the%20City%20of%20Joy%2C%20the%20first%20trickle%20of%20guests%20begins%20to%20enter%20the%20Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%2C%20which%20is%20carrying%20the%20baton%20of%20its%20legacy%20forward%2C%20not%20just%20in%20its%20food%20but%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294513%2Frare-pictures-of-india-history-freedom-struggle-independence-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20tales%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20every%20guest%20is%20treated%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711973034000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D344968%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Swadhin%20Bharat%20Hindu%20Hotel%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20started%20by%20Mangobindo%20Panda%2C%20is%20a%20century-old%20pice%20hotel%20where%20Indian%20freedom%20fighters%20like%20Netaji%20Subhas%20Chandra%20Bose%20would%20enjoy%20Bengali%20delicacies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Krystelle%20Dsouza%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344968%2Fswadhin-bharat-hindu-pice-hotel-kolkata-bengali-cuisine-netaji-subhas-chandra-bose-history%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22With%20a%20Turnover%20of%20Rs%203%20Crore%2C%20Couple%20Has%20Made%20Over%20a%20Million%20Eco-Friendly%20Bags%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhile